HEADWORD: Eyelash
<hw>Eye"lash`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The
fringe of hair that edges the eyelid; -- usually in the
<pluf>pl.</pluf></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A hair of the fringe on the edge of the
eyelid.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Eyeless</ent>⟦br⟧
